.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Electronics worker holding silicon wafer by cutting machine in clean room\" data-id=\"556415443\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5242px\" height=\"3932px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I presented my \u201cStrong Buy\u201d <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4708121-on-semiconductor-q2-volkswagen-deals-prove-sic-market-growth-potential\">thesis</a> for <b>ON Semiconductor Corporation</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ON\" title=\"ON Semiconductor Corporation\">ON</a></span>) in July 2024, emphasizing the challenges of destocking activities in the automotive and industrial markets. ON Semiconductor delivered 2% sequential revenue growth for </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741585-on-semiconductor-q3-remain-soft-in-automotive-and-industrial", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 00:01:40"}, {"id": "4741584", "title": "The Real Brokerage: An Impressive Disruptor, Expensive Valuation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view over houses in Paris suburb\" data-id=\"1500297506\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gary Yeowell</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>Real Brokerage (